BIG news, Explorers! We’re positively buzzing with excitement to let you know that Core Keeper new update is coming in January 28th 2026 on PS4 and PS5!

Awaken as an explorer in a long-forgotten cavern teeming with treasures and secrets. Harvest relics and resources, craft advanced tools, build your base, and explore over 10 unique biomes in a dynamically evolving world just waiting to be unearthed. Cultivate crops, fish in mysterious waters, master recipes, hatch pets, raise cattle, drive vehicles, fight enemies, level up your skills, automate your bases, and defeat legendary Titans to unveil the power of the Core.
